--- !u!114 &1624286992
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1624286990}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: dab40134f96b0c04e893ef68ca62f8c8, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::GameManager01
  dialogue_text01: {fileID: 160245424}
  character_text01: {fileID: 1872523126}
  dialogue01:
  - char_name: Chryseis
    dialogue_text: So, what do you do with your time?
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: Oh, uh, I research mythical creatures actually . . . like yourself
      . . .
    options: []
  - char_name: Chryseis
    dialogue_text: "That\u2019s cool! What can you tell me about Sirens then!"
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: Uhm, humans describe you as having humans as part of your diet,
      and you guys lure them in by singing . . . and uh . . .
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: (Actually, now that I think about it, should I be scared to be
      so close to a Siren?)
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: ". . . you\u2019re not gonna eat me, are you?"
    options: []
  - char_name: Chryseis
    dialogue_text: "Hahaha! You\u2019re funny!"
    options: []
  - char_name: Chryseis
    dialogue_text: "What you know isn\u2019t COMPLETELY baseless, I know a lot of
      my siblings do eat humans, but I think humans are way too interesting to eat."
    options: []
  - char_name: Chryseis
    dialogue_text: "Fish do just fine, in my opinion. There\u2019s plenty of them
      too!"
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: Do your siblings . . . encourage you to eat humans?
    options: []
  - char_name: Chryseis
    dialogue_text: "A couple of them, but they\u2019ve realised by now that I\u2019m
      not really interested in doing that, so they stopped talking to me about it. "
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: "(I\u2019m still scared)"
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: Oh, uhm, right . . .
    options: []
  - char_name: Chryseis
    dialogue_text: "Here, how about I hold your hand, and if I don\u2019t react to
      it at all, you should be able to trust that I won\u2019t eat you. Right?"
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: I mean not quite . . . you could be playing the long game here-
    options: []
  line_index01: 0
